      context: 'Birling represents Edwardian laissez-faire capitalism \u2014 the belief that social responsibility is an individual choice, not a collective duty. The 1945 audience knew this worldview led to two world wars, mass unemployment, and the Depression. Priestley makes the audience distrust Birling from the start so they reject his philosophy before the Inspector even arrives.',
